        <section id="overview">
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>
            The <strong>Fighting Game Performance Index (FGPI)</strong> is a single number that summarizes a player's overall competitive strength in Street Fighter 6.
            <em>Rankings</em> tell you <strong>who placed where</strong>. <em>FGPI</em> estimates <strong>how strong a player is right now</strong> by considering results along with
            <a href="/analytics-glossary/#consistency">consistency</a>,
            <a href="/analytics-glossary/#momentum">recent form</a>, and
            <a href="/analytics-glossary/#schedule-difficulty">event context / schedule difficulty</a> (see also
            <a href="/analytics-glossary/#t3r">T3R</a> and
            <a href="/analytics-glossary/#performance-floor">Performance Floor</a>).
          </p>
        </section>

